name: GAN NIGHT
description:
1am Berlin. Go to sleep. No, one more GAN run.  Image number 120, ok this face is actually...me...lost train of thought between different loops of text, audio, and visuals...what was the last model I was on...is it ready yet...no wait I was waiting for 2 to finish.  

I might burn this in the morning.
Maybe I'll keep it here...so every time I'm back here, this face reminds me...MACHINES NEED TO SLEEP TOO.

g'night

1024 x 1024
